'''雷東達龍屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Redondasaurus''）是種已滅絕[[植龍目|植龍目]]，生存於[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]晚期的[[北美洲|北美洲]]。雷東達龍是在1993年由Hunt與Lucas命名，只包含一個種 ''R. gregorii''。屬名是以[[美國|美國]][[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]的[[雷東達組|雷東達組]]（Redonda Formation）為名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dinosauria.com/dml/names/phyto.htm#R|title=Phytosauria Translation and Pronunciaton Guide|last=Creisler|first=Ben|date=1996-01-01|work=Dinosauria.com|accessdate=2008-04-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070328204157/http://www.dinosauria.com/dml/names/phyto.htm#R|archivedate=2007-03-28}}</ref>。雷東達龍是最晚出現、最衍化的植龍類<ref>''Late Palaeozoic and Early Mesozoic Circum-Pacific Events and their Global Correlation'' (World and Regional Geology); page 219. By J. M. Dickins, Yang Zunyi, Yin Hongfu, and S. G. Lucas. Published 1997, Cambridge University Press. ISBN 0521471753 Retrieved on 2008-04-24</ref>。

7雷東達龍是種大型[[肉食性|肉食性]]動物，頭顱骨長1.5公尺，根據估計，身長約7~11公尺，而高度約1.5公尺，體重估計值約11.7公噸<ref name="Dinos Alive!">{{cite web|url=http://www.dinosalive.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=23&Itemid=34|title=Dinos Alive official website's page on ''Redondasaurus''|publisher=www.dinosalive.com|accessdate=2008-04-24|archive-date=2008-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080520060507/http://dinosalive.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=23&Itemid=34|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。生活的大部分時間可能待在湖泊、河流，採伏擊方式攻擊獵物。雷東達龍的牙齒有少許[[琺瑯質|琺瑯質]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gsa.confex.com/gsa/2007AM/finalprogram/abstract_127709.htm |title=Tooth Enamel Microstructure of Selected Archosaurs Reptilia: Archosauria from the Upper Triassic Chinle Group, Western USA: Taxonomic and Evolutionary Significance |publisher=Andrew B. Heckert and Jessica Camp; Dept. of Geology, Appalachian State University |date=2007-10-31 |accessdate=2008-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608153333/http://gsa.confex.com/gsa/2007AM/finalprogram/abstract_127709.htm |archive-date=2011-06-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2002年的[[系統發生學|系統發生學]]研究發現，[[偽帕拉鱷|偽帕拉鱷]]、[[迷鱷|迷鱷]]、雷東達龍、[[尼克羅龍|尼克羅龍]]屬於[[偽帕拉鱷亞科|偽帕拉鱷亞科]]<ref name="Hungerbühler, 2002">Hungerbühler A. 2002. The Late Triassic phytosaur ''Mystriosuchus westphali'', with a revision of the genus. ''Palaeontology'' '''45''' (2): 377-418</ref>。

